---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms" description="Terms overview for Support Youth DJs shared platform, under-18 directory, public links, moderation, resources, merchandise, and affiliate disclosures.">
  <section class="page-head">
    <div class="page-head-inner">
      <p class="stamp">Terms</p>
      <h1>Terms Overview</h1>
      <p class="lead">Support Youth DJs is building a shared platform for youth DJ culture through directory participation, learning resources, editorial content, public links, and culture coverage.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="kicker">Draft terms language for legal review.</p>
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="panel red"><h2>No Guarantees</h2><p>Participation, directory listing, editorial coverage, contributor involvement, partnerships, purchases, or links do not guarantee bookings, sponsorships, media coverage, followers, income, or career outcomes.</p></article>
        <article class="panel"><h2>Directory Eligibility</h2><p>The directory is for DJs under 18. DJs ages 13-17 may initiate submissions. DJs under 13 require parent or legal guardian submission. Adults are not eligible for directory profiles.</p></article>
        <article class="panel"><h2>Review and Moderation</h2><p>Directory profiles, public links, and editorial connections are reviewed before publication. Support Youth DJs may decline, edit, correct, or remove content at its discretion.</p></article>
        <article class="panel"><h2>Public Links and Resources</h2><p>Directory submissions use public URLs only. External resources and public links may lead to third-party sites with their own rules, privacy practices, and content standards.</p></article>
        <article class="panel"><h2>Merchandise</h2><p>Merchandise, if activated, is a product purchase and not a donation. Product details, checkout, shipping, returns, and refund terms may be handled by outside providers.</p></article>
        <article class="panel"><h2>Affiliate Links</h2><p>Some links may be affiliate links. Support Youth DJs may earn a commission if a purchase is made through those links, at no extra cost to the visitor.</p></article>
      </div>
      <ul class="list"><li>Do not submit private personal information for publication.</li><li>Directory participation is separate from Spotlight or editorial coverage.</li><li>This overview is not final legal advice and should be reviewed before commerce, expanded submissions, or paid advertising begin.</li></ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
